<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Fifi Box appeared downcast as she attended an appointment in Melbourne following the death of her daughter Trixie's half-sister Jaimi Kenny at the age of 33.</p>

<p>The radio host wore a black face mask as she exited a dermatologist's office on Tuesday, carrying a piece of paper. </p>

<p>The 43-year-old was dressed in all black, including a pair of loose black three-quarter trousers. </p>

<p>Low mood: Fifi Box (pictured) appeared downcast as she attended an appointment in Melbourne following the death of her daughter Trixie's half-sister Jaimi Kenny at the age of 33</p>

<p>She added a shirt and flowing cardigan over the top, in the same dark tones, and more multi-print flats. </p>

<p>Fifi appeared makeup-free and had a large pair of sunglasses covering up her famous face.   </p>

<p>She appeared in low spirits, raising her hand to her face as she walked to her car.  </p>

<p>Exit: The radio host wore a black face mask as she exited a dermatologist's office on Tuesday, carrying a piece of paper</p>

<p>Dark days: The 43-year-old was dressed in all black, including a pair of loose black three-quarter trousers</p>

<p>The radio star pulled out of her breakfast radio show earlier on Tuesday following news that Jaimi had died.</p>

<p>Her absence was briefly alluded to on Fox FM's Fifi, Fev and Byron, with host Byron Cooke saying: 'Well, Fi is away today but the show must go on.'  </p>

<p>Fifi welcomed Trixie, seven, in 2013 after a brief relationship with Jaimi's father, Ironman Grant Kenny. </p>

<p>Sad days: She appeared in low spirits, raising her hand to her face as she walked to her car</p>

<p>Break: The radio star pulled out of her breakfast radio show earlier on Tuesday following news that Jaimi had died</p>

<p>Despite their break-up remained close to Grant's children from his previous marriage to Lisa Curry: Jaimi, Morgan and Jett.  </p>

<p>She hasn't commented publicly on Jaimi's death, but it's believed they were close.</p>

<p>Jaimi's mother, three-time Olympian Lisa Curry, separated from Grant in 2009 after 23 years of marriage, before finalising their divorce in 2017.  </p>

<p>It comes after Lisa released a heartbreaking statement about the death of her eldest child on Tuesday.</p>

<p>Family: Fifi welcomed Trixie, seven, (right) in 2013 after a brief relationship with Jaimi's father, Ironman Grant Kenny. She hasn't commented publicly on Jaimi's death, but it's believed they were close</p>

<p>Past: Jaimi's mother, three-time Olympian Lisa Curry, separated from Grant in 2009 after 23 years of marriage, before finalising their divorce in 2017. All pictured in 2008</p>

<p> Tragic: It comes after Lisa released a heartbreaking statement about the death of her eldest child on Tuesday. Lisa is pictured with Jami </p>

<p>The 58-year-old former competitive swimmer spoke of her 'unbearable' pain in a gut-wrenching Instagram post.</p>

<p>'Our hearts are completely broken. Our beautiful daughter Jaimi has lost her battle with a long-term illness and passed away peacefully in hospital yesterday morning with her loving family by her side,' Lisa wrote.  </p>

<p>'I just can't believe you're not here anymore. I sit and just shake my head. It doesn't seem real or right. You will forever be with me in my heart, Jaimi. I love you so much.' </p>

<p>The 58-year-old spoke of her 'unbearable' pain in a gut-wrenching Instagram post: 'Our hearts are completely broken. Our beautiful daughter Jaimi has lost her battle with a long-term illness and passed away peacefully in hospital yesterday' she wrote </p>
